com.siperian.bdd.userexits.datamodel

  • Packages that use com.siperian.bdd.userexits.datamodel 
    Package Description
    com.siperian.bdd.userexits.datamodel
    Defines the data objects used for IDD user exits.
    com.siperian.bdd.userexits.operations
    Interfaces to implement to implement user exits (costom functionality) for a IDD application.
